# Never ship dependencies, VCS metadata, secrets or docs into an image.
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log*
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.github

# Secrets / local env — must never end up in an image layer
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/secret*.yaml
!infra/k8s/04-secret.example.yaml

# Build / infra artifacts not needed at runtime
docs
infra/k8s
scripts
compose.yaml
compose.*.yaml
**/Containerfile
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore

# Editor / OS noise
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/coverage
**/*.md
